name: Master_Pipeline
description: The PL_MASTER_CHILD pipeline loads data from the master_child_export-YYYYMMDD.csv file in the data lake into the MASTER_CHILD SQL table. It extracts the date from the filename, adds it as an ingestion_date column, truncates the table to remove old data, and then loads the new data using a Mapping Data Flow.
